  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sirohi District Social Inclusion</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project focuses on promoting equal opportunities environment for disabled people in the district by integrating social inclusion approach 

In addition to ensuring basic rehabilitation (including social and education) for visually impaired people, the project will strengthen capacities of VI people on accessing and undertaking livelihood initiatives. The project will also develop leaders among disabled people in the district who will take lead in advocating for their members rights. 

So as to develop an enabling environment, the project will sensitise and support wider stakeholders in mainstreaming disability in all their development programmes.</narrative>
  </description>
